---
title: Oven-Ready Soy-Glazed Chicken with Broccoli & Buttery Rice (trays included)
description: What do we love more than a delicious, home-cooked dinner? A delicious, home-cooked dinner that doesn’t require any prep OR dirtying multiple dishes! This week’s meal is just that. Sticky, savory-sweet chicken is served with buttery rice and sesame-studded broccoli—and it’s all ready in just 20 minutes. Now that’s a weeknight win!
